l/Voiceover:**\n    *   **Google Maps Platform:** Show a mapping app highlighting features. \"Need location services? The Google Maps API is a dev's best friend!\"\n    *   **Firebase:** Show a simple chat app receiving messages. \"Building real-time apps? Firebase offers powerful backend services with ease.\"\n    *   **Gemini API (or TensorFlow/Vertex AI):** Show a clever AI feature in an app. \"Or integrate cutting-edge AI directly into your projects with Gemini!\"\n*   **(18-25s) Visual:** Quick montage of different Google API/SDK logos. \"These 'Google ADKs' are empowering developers to create the future, one amazing feature at a time.\"\n*   **(25-30s) CTA:** \"Which Google developer kit are YOU excited to explore?\"\n\n**Suggested Hashtags:**\n#GoogleAPIs #Firebase #GeminiAPI #DeveloperKits #TechInnovation #GoogleDev #FutureTech #AIforDevs #BuildAmazingThings #TechTrends\n\n---\n\n### Reel Idea 3: Your First Step: Building Apps with Google's FREE Developer Tools!\n\n**Hook Line:** \"Dreaming of building your own app? Here's how to start with Google's accessible 'ADK' tools!\"\n\n**Quick Script Idea:**\n*   **(0-5s) Visual:** A person excitedly sketching app ideas in a notebook or on a tablet.\n*   **(5-10s) Voiceover/Text:** \"Ready to turn your app idea into reality? You don't need to be a pro. Google offers awesome, free tools to get started!\"\n*   **(10-20s) Visual:** Focus on Firebase as an example.\n    *   Show a quick visual of signing up for Firebase. \"Start with Firebase \u2013 Google's all-in-one backend for your app!\"\n    *   Show a snippet of setting up authentication or adding a simple database entry. \"No need to build your own servers; Firebase handles authentication, databases, hosting, and more.\"\n*   **(20-25s) Visual:** Show a simple, functional app that leverages Firebase (e.g., a simple to-do list, a chat app). \"It helps you launch your app faster, focusing on the cool features users will love!\"\n*   **(25-30s) CTA:** \"Grab your laptop, head to Firebase.google.com, and start building your dream app today!\"\n\n**Suggested Hashtags:**\n#LearnToCode #BeginnerDev #FirebaseTutorial #AppBuilding #CodingTips #GoogleForDevs #NoCode (if highlighting certain Firebase features that simplify coding) #TechForBeginners #DeveloperJourney"}], "role": "model"}, "finish_reason": "STOP", "usage_metadata": {"candidates_token_count": 1062, "candidates_tokens_details": [{"modality": "TEXT", "token_count": 1062}], "prompt_token_count": 64, "prompt_tokens_details": [{"modality": "TEXT", "token_count": 64}], "thoughts_token_count": 1290, "total_token_count": 2416, "traffic_type": "ON_DEMAND"}, "avg_logprobs": -1.062437470574388, "invocation_id": "e-41529008-24fa-4eee-aeca-329bcce30aee", "author": "InstagramAgent", "actions": {"state_delta": {"instagram_content": "Here are 3 Instagram Reel ideas focusing on Google's Developer Kits, assuming \"Google ADK\" refers broadly to their **Android Development Kit (SDK)** and other powerful developer tools.\n\n---\n\n### Reel Idea 1: Demystifying \"Google ADK\" - Your Android App Builder!\n\n**Hook Line:** \"Ever wonder how your favorite Android apps come to life? It's all thanks to Google's 'ADK'!\"\n\n**Quick Script Idea:**\n*   **(0-3s) Visual:** Start with a quick, dynamic montage of popular Android apps on different devices.\n*   **(3-8s) Voiceover/Text:** \"When people say 'Google ADK,' they're often talking about the **Android SDK (Software Development Kit)**!\"\n*   **(8-15s) Visual:** Show quick cuts of Android Studio IDE, a line of code being written, then instantly appearing on an emulator/device. \"This is the core toolkit devs use to build almost every app on your Android phone.\"\n*   **(15-25s) Visual:** Highlight key SDK components: emulator running, drag-and-drop UI designer, debugging. \"From designing sleek interfaces to making your app run smoothly, the Android SDK provides all the building blocks.\"\n*   **(25-30s) CTA:** \"Want to build your own app? Sta